title: War of the Roses: He Went To Visit His Mom In Montevideo
description: Kim's boyfriend went to go visit his mom in Montevideo for the day. He all of a sudden told her he's staying 'the whole weekend'. She got worried and brought him to War Of The Roses to get to the bottom of what's going on.
